namespace("kap")
m вҶҗ map "" "
  fhelp: info about Kap functions

  try the following: 

  ]fhelp primitives - see the list of primitives
  ]fhelp <primitive> - help about each primitive, eg. help вҹҰ
  ]fhelp namespaces - see the list of namespaces
  ]fhelp <namespace> - more info about each namespace and their functions  
"
