  TILDE DIAERESIS вҚЁ

  Keyboard: `T

  Monadic operator (FвҚЁ x): Duplicate, derives a monadic function that calls F dyadically with x as arguments.
 
  Dyadic operator (x FвҚЁ y): Commute, derives a function which calls the underlying function with the arguments reversed. 

