  JOT DIAERESIS вҚӨ

  Keyboard: `J

  Dyadic operator: Rank, (fвҚӨa) applies its left operand function to cells of its arguments specified by its 
  right operand array. The right operand specifies the rank of subarrays to which the left operand function is 
  applied as follows: For left argument вҚә and right argument вҚө,

   вҚӨ    c   вҚқ Rank-c cells of вҚө (monadic) or both arguments (dyadic)
   вҚӨ  b c   вҚқ Rank-b cells of вҚә and rank-c cells of вҚө (dyadic)
   вҚӨa b c   вҚқ Rank-a cells of вҚө (monadic), b-cells of вҚә and c-cells of вҚө (dyadic)
  
  вҠў mвҶҗ3 3вҚҙвҚі9 вӢ„ vвҶҗ10 20 30                 v +вҚӨ1 вҠўm     вҚқ 1-cells + 1-cells
0 1 2                                   10 21 32
3 4 5                                   13 24 35
6 7 8                                   16 27 38
