  DEL DIAERESIS вҚў

  Keyboard: `G

  Dyadic operator: Under, takes two functions. When called as AвҚўB x, the function B is first called on x, 
  and the return value is passed to A. The effect of B is then reversed.

  (10+)вҚў(2вҶ‘) 3 3 вҚҙ вҚі9  вҚқ takes 2 top rows, adds 10 to them and then puts back the bottom row
в”ҢвҶ’в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
вҶ“10 11 12в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ13 14 15в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 6  7  8в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
"
